'''中国台湾'''（{{lang-en|Taiwan, China}}）或'''中国台湾省'''（[[ISO_3166-1|ISO 3166-1]]代码：TW{{NoteTag| [[台湾|台湾]]在国际标准ISO 3166-1和[[ISO_3166-2:TW|ISO 3166-2:TW]]中使用“中国台湾省”之名称。并另被編入[[ISO_3166-2:CN|ISO 3166-2:CN]]中，代碼為{{mono|CN-TW}}。}}<ref name="USA2012">{{cite book|author=International Business Publications, USA|title=Taiwan Country Study Guide Strategic Information and Developments|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=XghBi4moFK4C&pg=PA48|date=3 March 2012|publisher=Int'l Business Publications|language=en|isbn=978-1-4387-7570-8|page=48|quote=The issue of TOC's name came under scrutiny during the 2006 World Baseball Classic. The organizers of the 16-team tournament intended to call Taiwan as such, but reverted to "Chinese Taipei" under pressure from PRC. The ROC protested the decision, claiming that the WBC is not an IOC event, but did not prevail. The ISO 3166 directory of names of countries and territories registers Taiwan (TW) sepeartely from and in addition to the People's Republic of China, but lists Taiwan as "Taiwan, Province of China" based on the name used by the UN under PRC pressure. In ISO 3166-2:CN, Taiwan is also coded CN-71 under China, thus making Taiwan part of China in ISO 3166-1 and ISO 3166-2 categories.}}</ref><ref name="faqs_specific"/>；{{lang-en|Taiwan, Province of China}}<!-- 非Taiwan, Republic of China --><ref name="EN">{{cite web|url=https://www.iso.org/obp/ui/#iso:code:3166:TW|title=ISO 3166 — Codes for the representation of names of countries and their subdivisions|work=[[ISO|ISO]]|language=en|access-date=2018-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617031837/https://www.iso.org/obp/ui/#iso:code:3166:TW|archive-date=2016-06-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>；{{lang-fr|Taïwan, Province de Chine}}<!-- 非Taïwan, République de Chine --><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.iso.org/obp/ui/fr/#iso:code:3166:TW|title=ISO 3166 — Codes pour la représentation des noms de pays et de leurs subdivisions|work=[[ISO|ISO]]|language=fr|access-date=2018-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140805092610/https://www.iso.org/obp/ui/fr/#iso:code:3166:TW|archive-date=2014-08-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>），是国际标准[[ISO_3166-1|ISO 3166-1]]下[[台灣|台灣]]的名称<ref name="faqs_specific"/>，也是[[联合国|联合国]]、[[世界经济论坛|世界经济论坛]]、[[国际标准化组织|国际标准化组织]]、[[世界银行|世界银行]]、[[国际货币基金组织|国际货币基金组织]]等国际组织对台湾的主要称呼<ref name=联合国甲/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.un.org/chinese/News/story.asp?NewsID=25624|title=潘基文对中国台湾省地震表示关切|date=2016-02-09|publisher=聯合國|access-date=2016-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220103307/http://www.un.org/chinese/News/story.asp?NewsID=25624|archive-date=2016-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=联合国乙>{{cite web|url=http://www.un.org/chinese/News/story.asp?NewsID=6868|title=中国台湾林义杰为联合国跑越撒哈拉|date=2006-11-28|publisher=聯合國開發計劃署|access-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911064401/http://www.un.org/chinese/News/story.asp?NewsID=6868|archive-date=2016-09-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=联合国丙>{{cite web|url=http://www.un.org/en/development/desa/policy/wesp/wesp_current/2016wesp_pr_ea_ch.pdf|title=联合国报告:东亚与南亚的经济增长将小幅提高|quote=去年中国台湾省以及中国香港特别行政区受困於出口不振。在2016-2017年，预计出口回升以及稳定的个人消费会导致这两个经济体的增长温和复苏。缅甸和越南是东亚经济在2015年的亮点，而其中的支撑因素，包括新投资以及稳健的个人消费，都预期会持续存在。|publisher=聯合國新聞部|access-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160519222910/http://www.un.org/en/development/desa/policy/wesp/wesp_current/2016wesp_pr_ea_ch.pdf|archive-date=2016-05-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=联合国丁>{{cite news|url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1037918|title=聲明誤用中華台北 WEF改回中國台灣|date=2016-10-03|newspaper=自由時報|language=zh|author=呂伊萱|location=臺北市|access-date=2016-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161003172351/http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1037918|archive-date=2016-10-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201610020249-1.aspx|title=聲明誤用中華台北 WEF改回中國台灣|date=2016-10-02|author=江今葉|location=布魯塞爾|language=zh|agency=中央通訊社|access-date=2016-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170104223216/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201610020249-1.aspx|archive-date=2017-01-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="矮化甲"/><ref name="USA2012"/><ref name="IMF甲">{{cite web|author1=IMF|title=亚洲经济增长的回升为改革提供了机遇|url=http://www.imf.org/zh/News/Articles/2017/10/12/NA101317-For-Asia-Growth-Pickup-Provides-Opportunity-for-Reforms|website=国际货币基金组织|accessdate=2018-07-10|location=|language=zh-hans|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630183210/http://www.imf.org/zh/News/Articles/2017/10/12/NA101317-For-Asia-Growth-Pickup-Provides-Opportunity-for-Reforms|archive-date=2018-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="世行甲">{{cite web|author1=世界银行|title=中国台湾 营商环境|url=http://chinese.doingbusiness.org/data/exploreeconomies/taiwan-china|website=国际银行|accessdate=2018-07-10|location=|language=zh-hans|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710071345/http://chinese.doingbusiness.org/data/exploreeconomies/taiwan-china|archive-date=2018-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦是[[中华人民共和国政府|中华人民共和国政府]]在国际和国内场合中对[[台湾|台湾]]的正式称呼之一。

